/**
 * MP3 Player — Nintendo Switch Homebrew
 * Stack: libnx + SDL2 + SDL2_image + SDL2_mixer + nlohmann/json  (C++17)
 *
 * Theme system
 * ─────────────
 * On startup the app scans  romfs:/themes/  for subdirectories that contain
 * a  theme.json  file (generated by tools/theme_editor/).
 * If none are found it falls back to the built-in "default" palette (no
 * assets required — pure colour rectangles).
 *
 * The theme-selector screen is shown with  Y  from the main screen.
 * Navigate with DPad Up/Down, confirm with A, go back with B.
 */

